name: "Haunted Quack!" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description:
[Paint pen, metallic marker, felt pen, and foam letters on reclaimed cardboard with digital embellishments and color.] The séance went well, despite the fact that the snakes had no hands to move the planchette and the duck's feathers were constantly being ruffled by strange, unearthly winds...

---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
